maining active beam counts to totalExited\n6. Returns totalExited as bigint\n\nKey insight: Instead of enumerating paths (exponential), we propagate path *counts* row by row (linear in grid size).\n\n**Step 2: Run build to verify it compiles**\n\nRun: `npm run build`\nExpected: PASS\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: Write unit tests\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `tests/beam.test.ts`\n\n**Step 1: Write tests covering the TASK.md examples and edge cases**\n\nTest cases:\n- Straight beam, no splitters -> 5 cells, 1 path\n- Single splitter example from TASK.md -> 5 cells, 2 paths\n- Two splitters example from TASK.md -> 6 cells, 4 paths\n- Edge splitter (beam absorbed) -> correct cell count\n- Empty grid (no source) -> 0 cells, 0n paths\n- Single-row grid -> 1 cell, 1n path\n- Single-column with splitter -> both beams absorbed\n\n**Step 2: Run tests**\n\nRun: `npm test`\nExpected: ALL PASS\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: Run full validation\n\n**Step 1: Run build**\n\nRun: `npm run build`\nExpected: PASS\n\n**Step 2: Run lint**\n\nRun: `npm run lint`\nExpected: PASS\n\n**Step 3: Run tests**\n\nRun: `npm test`\nExpected: ALL PASS\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":122,"cache_read_input_tokens":32414,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":122},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"83bbf23f-d080-4ebe-9bc9-5ee81b3d3078","uuid":"741429de-76bf-479b-9d9f-09a96ac8d476"}
