+- Two splitters example from TASK.md -> 6 cells, 4 paths
+- Edge splitter (beam absorbed) -> correct cell count
+- Empty grid (no source) -> 0 cells, 0n paths
+- Single-row grid -> 1 cell, 1n path
+- Single-column with splitter -> both beams absorbed
+
+**Step 2: Run tests**
+
+Run: `npm test`
+Expected: ALL PASS
+
+---
